      <flip type="script"><![CDATA[
        msg ("You flip the painting, and find a message written into the backboard.<br/><br/>The message says, \"I knew youd come looking for answers here first, in your shop. Find the place where the two lines converge. The place we parted every morning and reunited every evening. <br/><br/>But first, look in your safe. I know you never got around to using it, so I gave it a six digit code; but the code is simple. If I know you - and trust me I do - only you could figure it out. <br/><br/>Just remember when I told you to weigh your options carefully, before spending tens of thousands on property in the city. And you said, 'Location, location, location.' Turn the painting back when you're done. I dont want someone or something following you.<br/><br/>")
      ]]></flip>
